<s> WC Yes.  </s>
<s> WL We have to remember that the new WCAG will mostly be the old WCAG.  </s>
<s> Most of what we are working on is at the level of wording at the top part and how its organized.  </s>
<s> It will clearly contain the same guidelines and checkpoints.  </s>
