<s> LK Since OBJECT way of including Non-w3c standards, they wanted to remove possibility of including non-w3c stuff.  </s>
<s> WL no. there's other ways to get that stuff in.  </s>
<s> The main argument was that it had become too huge.  </s>
<s> Had too many attributes.  </s>
