<s> LK APPLET still deprecated?  </s>
<s> WC Then how include multimedia?  </s>
<s> Other option is EMBED but it is not part of any HTML spec.  </s>
<s> So, what would you use for Flash, etc?  </s>
<s> I guess SVG would be included with IMG? MC I thought it wasn't being implemented.  </s>
<s> WL No reason to drop.  </s>
<s> LK Think in IE. WC Possibly also communicator.  </s>
